snippet.title: Anniversary Update Trailer - Planet Coaster
snippet.description:
Celebrate a year of Planet Coaster with the free 1.4 Anniversary Update! The update brings the scenario editor, five new rides, new scenery items, management and UI improvements and much more!

For more news and information about Planet Coaster:

Website: https://planetcoaster.com/
Forums: https://forums.planetcoaster.com/
Facebook: https://facebook.com/PlanetCoaster
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlanetCoaster
